Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波浪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:49.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个  三十八度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误差0.2毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:57.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  请下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:05.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记录  78米23厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:08.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与指定位置的误差是54厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,综合评价大能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Level 4
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:17.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状态还是不怎么样啊  果然昨天风纪委员的工作影响到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:17.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(385,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:23.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借口那么多看来你也没什么本事哦  白井黑子同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:24.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚后光子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:29.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来先到达超能力者的人会是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:29.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:34.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别把我的能力跟你的相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:38.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且三次元跟十一次元的空间把握方法根本上就不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:44.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就看不惯你个一年级态度那么嚣张  明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子完全不把别人的话听进去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:47.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等本小姐成为常盘台王牌的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:50.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.19,0:07:00.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年才转学到二年级的你可能还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:06.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在那泳池里测试能力的就是常盘台的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:14.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有泳池的水缓冲的话  就无法正常计测的破坏力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:19.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有正面接下那一击的觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:26.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记录  炮弹初速  约为秒速1030m
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连发能力  每分钟8发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,着弹分布  18.9毫米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,综合评价超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  声音都传到校庭去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:55.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音那么大  大家都被吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:59.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  要是不用那种方法就无法正常计测
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.86,0:08:03.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我的能力  黑子的能力方便多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家花不如野花香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:12.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  姐姐大人都是常盘台的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大方地抬头挺胸就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.85,0:08:17.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么王牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:25.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说要挺  但这个胸却不够凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:30.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~不过这平坦才是姐姐的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:36.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这谦虚而又让人烦恼的诱惑  黑子要  黑子的心就要臣服了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打从娘胎出来就坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是交流感情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:44.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:09:01.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初~春~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天穿的是淡淡的粉红色点纹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:12.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突  突然对我干什么啊  佐天同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:17.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对同班同学用敬语  你还是那么见外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就让我们为增进感情再掀一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:29.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉我太得寸进尺了  作为补偿你也看看我的内裤怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:32.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  佐天同学真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:36.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:39.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是体检
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.53,0:09:42.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子低能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(365,328)\fs18}Level 1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:47.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小学开始就一直没进步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:51.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担当老师也说「你脑袋上的花只是用来看的吗？！」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:54.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「用你那花的开放力把你的能力也开放了吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:10:00.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我很想对那老师的说教吐槽几句
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还是打起精神来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且低能力者还不算坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(288,328)\fs18}Level 1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是Level 0——无能力者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过用不着在意这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:19.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要每天过得开心  就万事OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:21.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.47,0:10:24.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  听听这个打起精神来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:27.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「HITOTSUI HAJIME」这不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:30.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下载了先行发布的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:33.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是收录了这首曲子的专辑的发售日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明下载了还要买CD吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:38.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在初回限定版的应募券中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:44.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽中100名抽选额的豪华奖品才能称作真的FAN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一起去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:50.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我今天约了白井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:53.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学是风纪委员的那个白井黑子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:53.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:57.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她实现了我的愿望  让我跟御坂学姐见面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:01.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学园都市里也只有7名的超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:01.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:04.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘台的王牌御坂美琴同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘台的超能力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:06.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:11.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也是那种因为能力优秀就居高临下看人的讨人厌的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:12.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.01,0:11:19.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那种人一般都会小看比自己能力低的人吧  真气人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是什么常盘台的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.91,0:11:23.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好吗  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:27.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  就是大小姐才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:31.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊  只是憧憬有钱人而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没有这种事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:37.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一说  跟我出身西葛西也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:40.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  趁这机会佐天同学也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:45.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:46.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.25,0:11:48.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种机会很难得的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我等等  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的FAN？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:12:01.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在风纪委员的第177支部担当我的后援的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:12:01.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(185,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:06.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缠着我说就算一次也好要见姐姐大人一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:14.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道姐姐大人平时总是被FAN的无礼行为烦恼着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.12,0:12:19.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过初春是知道分寸的乖巧的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:23.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是我所认同的为数不多的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看在黑子的面子上见她一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:29.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我会尽力把姐姐大人的压力压制到最小限度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的预定就由我来好好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:32.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:38.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么  用初春当借口跟姐姐大人约会的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  在家庭餐厅增进感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:43.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  去内衣商店买决战内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:46.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三  去香水商店购物买媚药
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其四  驱逐初春
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其五  跟姐姐大人一起去宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:54.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你想利用乖巧又有分寸的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成就自己的变态愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:56.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:13:01.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是看到这些就让我积蓄了很多压力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:06.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼  原谅我吧  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:13.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然是黑子的朋友  那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:17.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:18.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人竟然这么看重黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:24.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子  黑子真是不知如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:24.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:30.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这样会打扰到其他客人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:36.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我先介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:41.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是栅川中学一年级的初春饰利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:45.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初…初次见面  我叫初春饰利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:50.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是初春的同班同学佐天泪子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:52.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就一起跟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:56.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提  我是无能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:56.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,328)\fs18}Level 0
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:57.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐…佐天同学你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学和佐天同学对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:03.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫御坂美琴  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:07.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.23,0:14:08.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:14.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  在繁琐的介绍之后  虽然和预定有些出入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:16.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的安排就由黑子我来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:17.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.74,0:14:18.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:24.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里也没什么事干  总之我们就先去游戏中心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游戏中心…么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.71,0:14:30.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  黑子  我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:40.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起打游戏和在书店蹭书看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:46.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就不能拥有些像插花及琴乐之类与您相得益彰的兴趣么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.31,0:14:47.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  我从哪里看上去像是和茶道及琴乐有缘的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:55.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得她完全就没有大小姐的样子么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:58.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也完全没有高高在上的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像新开了一家可丽饼店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:07.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是最早光临的100名客人可以得到呱呱太的吉祥公仔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:09.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种便宜货算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这年头哪还有人会吃这套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:13.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.17,0:15:17.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:21.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是不是对可丽饼感兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:25.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那个赠品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能会喜欢呱呱太嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想  那可是青蛙啊  两栖类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:35.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能有女生会喜欢这种东西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人可真不少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有那么多小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:59.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息时间是一个小时  大家千万别走远了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得真不巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去占个位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学  我们的那份就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:12.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱之后会付给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:12.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:16.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  需要换个位置吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:24.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换不换位置无所谓…我只要能买到可丽饼就心满意足了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  拿到呱呱太了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:28.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:34.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿好  这是最后一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:37.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…咦  最后一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:42.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:46.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话  这个就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:48.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不客气…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:02.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧姐姐大人  千万别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:06.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会是纳豆和奶油的搭配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.34,0:17:07.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:14.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂学姐  她虽然不怎么符合大小姐的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:17.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却是个比预想中要容易亲近得多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:21.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:26.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:27.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝吧  就当作是刚才的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一口尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:39.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人都已经有我了  竟然还去佐天同学那里沾花惹草
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你的那位朋友恐怕是水火不容了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:46.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  你看那家银行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明还是白天  为什么要把防盗卷帘门给放下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:17:59.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联系警备员以及确认伤员就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:02.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(230,328)\fs18}Anti-Skills
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:04.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:05.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:11.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维护学园都市的治安可是我们风纪委员的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:11.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:15.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次请您务必不要插手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:20.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  第七学区可丽饼店前的银行发生抢劫事件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求警备员出动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Anti-Skills
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  别磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:26.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抓紧的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是风纪委员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:30.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(338,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:35.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以「毁坏器物及抢劫现行犯」的罪名逮捕你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:44.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然来了个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纪委员也人手不足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:46.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:52.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不闪边的话  可是要受伤的哟…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:55.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种下三滥的台词…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是领便当的敲门砖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:03.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:05.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:08.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不可以了  现在从广场出去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:08.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.86,0:19:09.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:10.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:13.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个男孩子不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:17.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才  说去巴士取落下的东西后就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:20.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我和初春同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:20.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那我们分头找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今已经容不得让你后悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:36.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我认真起来  你就会像块炭一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:35.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发火能力者  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:35.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(274,303)\fs18}Pyrokinesister
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:38.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:38.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:41.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.87,0:19:42.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:43.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间移动能力者？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,328)\fs18}Teleporter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:59.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还妄想反抗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:04.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把这个直接转移到你体内哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:06.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底跑到哪里去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:13.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是从哪里冒出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:18.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  大哥哥你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你过来就老老实实赶快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:21.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:26.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看还是再去广场找…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干什么  放手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:30.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.13,0:20:30.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:37.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:44.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是我个人的干架
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:49.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我要出手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:54.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了  传闻中被风纪委员逮捕就意味着人生的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:54.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(305,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:58.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有一个腹黑到家的空间移动能力者来把你的身心蹂躏到崩溃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:58.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Teleporter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嘴里说的是谁来着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:03.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  怎能就这样撒腿就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:05.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更有甚者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:11.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有个能把那个空间移动能力者驯得服服帖帖的最强的电击使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:11.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,328)\fs18}Teleporter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.87,0:21:11.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,328)\fs18}Electro Master
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:15.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我把你们都给解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:22.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  她就是站在学园都市230万人之巅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:25.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7名超能力者的第三位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:25.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,328)\fs18}Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:41.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超电磁炮——御坂美琴姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:41.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,328)\fs18}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:48.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是常盘台中学引以为豪  天下无敌的电击公主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:02.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:03.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:16.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般平民没有负伤者出现  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:18.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请你们走快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:23.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的能力也不赖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:27.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在强能力者左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.98,0:22:27.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,328)\fs18}Level 3
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:32.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你是由于自满于自己的能力而迷失了方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.75,0:22:37.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你好好反省自己  回头是岸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.85,0:22:44.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.85,0:22:46.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:48.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不知道该怎么感谢你才好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:49.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.44,0:22:52.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功一件呢  佐天同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:09.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很帅气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.26,0:23:15.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御坂学姐也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.21,0:23:17.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:18.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:22.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学  你的伤不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.41,0:23:23.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:25.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下去
